34  // Outputs the final standings and results after the session is over
35  private void AfterSession(ISessionDataProvider sessionData)
36  {
37  int i = 0;
38 
39  // Header and update time
40  Console.WriteLine("# Standings");
41  Console.WriteLine();
42  Console.WriteLine($"Last update: {DateTime.Now.ToString("R")}");
43  Console.WriteLine();
44 
45  // Classification
46  Console.WriteLine("## Classification");
47  Console.WriteLine();
48  Console.WriteLine("| Pos. | AI Thinker | Points |");
49  Console.WriteLine("|:----:| ---------- | -----: |");
50  foreach (KeyValuePair<string, int> tp in sessionData.Standings)
51  {
52  Console.WriteLine($"| {++i} | {tp.Key} | {tp.Value} |");
53  }
54  Console.WriteLine();
55 
56  // Results
57  Console.WriteLine("## Results");
58  Console.WriteLine();
59  Console.WriteLine("_Winner, if any, shown in bold_");
60  Console.WriteLine();
61  Console.WriteLine("| White | Red |");
62  Console.WriteLine("| -----:|:------- |");
63  foreach (KeyValuePair<Match, Winner> mw in sessionData.Results)
64  {
65  string white = $"`{mw.Key.thinkerWhite}`";
66  string red = $"`{mw.Key.thinkerRed}`";
67  if (mw.Value == Winner.White) white = $"**{white}**";
68  else if (mw.Value == Winner.Red) red = $"**{red}**";
69  Console.WriteLine($"| {white} | {red} |");
70  }
71  }
